00:13:09.000 --> 00:13:15.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
<i>Theodore Levin</i>: And then you ended up - how many years were you living in Pakistan before you came to Fremont?

00:13:15.000 --> 00:13:19.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
<i>Homayoun Sakhi</i>: Uh... I think from '92 til 2001.

00:13:19.000 --> 00:13:22.000 line:13 position:0% align:left size:100% background:black color:white
